headline: Poshmark, Inc. Appoints First Chief Product Officer
summary: Poshmark, a leading fashion resale marketplace powered by a vibrant community and real-time social experiences, today announced the appointment of Heather Friedland as its first Chief Product Officer. In this role, Friedland will be responsible for leading the company's product strategy, roadmap and execution, helping drive Poshmark's next phase of innovation and growth. Her first day with the company is today.

headline: Why The Narrative Around eBay Is Shifting After Recent Analyst and Business Updates
summary: eBay’s consensus analyst price target has seen a modest uptick, rising from $89 to approximately $91.55 per share. This adjustment reflects an evolving mix of optimism and caution among analysts, as debates continue about the company’s growth prospects and market positioning. Stay tuned to see how you can follow the latest shifts in eBay’s narrative and remain informed on analyst sentiment as it changes.
